                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/991" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MIS-0053</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9689 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">第三方支付平台的“隐忧”与“外患”——以支付宝为例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐艳，康丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">支付宝（中国）网络技术有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科研、咨询业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">第三方支付平台；支付宝；滞留资金；金融监管</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Third-party payment platform; Alipay; retention funds; financial supervision</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着电子商务的迅猛发展，第三方支付平台已经成为发展形势最快的方式，而其中支付宝又是最引人关注的一个第三方支付平台，其市场份额之大，现金流之多都远远超出了人们的预期。然而，支付宝在面临着前所未有的发展机遇的同时，也承受着巨大的压力和忧患。随着第三方支付业务许可证的发放，未来监管政策仍然会给第三方支付企业带来很大的不确定性，尤其是滞留资金存在的风险。本案例透过分析支付宝股权风波和其在2011年遭到的挤兑事件的起因与过程，探讨第三方支付平台存在的风险。第三方支付企业如何在这次洗牌机会中胜出？如何不被政策监管和激烈的市场竞争淘汰，如何防范和应对风险，本案例具有重要的借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2010 June, the central bank introduced &quot;Administrative Measures for the Payment Services Provided By Non-financial Institutions&quot;, which involves the third-party payment business. Under no the central bank approval, any non-financial institutions and individuals shall not engage in or disguise in payment business. Along with the  development of the electronic payment in our country, the third party payment has become the fastest way, which Alipay is most noticeable in the third party payment, and it caused the industry’s attention and comments to VIE mode Alipay has driven the development of the domestic online payment, but the &quot;approach&quot; initiates the changes of the Alipay ownership structure, and aroused great concern in by the industry, and as issuance of the third party payment business license, future regulatory policy will still give the third party payment companies a great uncertainty, especially the retention money risk. Through the analysis of the case of Alipay disturbance and the run events happened in 2011,we analysis the risk on the third party payment platform. How the third party payment companies can win in this shuffle. How not to be eliminated by the policy regulation and the fierce market competition. How to prevent and respond to the risk, this case has important significance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《电子商务》、《财务管理》、《管理学》、《公司金融》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">第三方支付平台内部控制形式、基本的运营方式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012-10</td>
                            </tr>
